  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR SOCIAL MEDIA</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/8a1f8fe61febe79e5c2f40979323cf7c.avif?t=1773306304\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dusty Derby is a large online multiplayer party royal game with 32 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute Dusts Compete to be King of Dusts in various places in the house!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/a8d9096b663ed9038c7dd58907336ff3.poster.avif?t=1773306304\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/a8d9096b663ed9038c7dd58907336ff3.webm?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/a8d9096b663ed9038c7dd58907336ff3.mp4?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/4f346e7139f33777cffea503acda7098.avif?t=1773306304\" width=616 height=123 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight! Throw! Win! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party up with your friends and have fun together! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat other players and be the last one standing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/430a28230143cc3bb39aef7c395368c2.poster.avif?t=1773306304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/430a28230143cc3bb39aef7c395368c2.webm?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/430a28230143cc3bb39aef7c395368c2.mp4?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/8ae454bbff8d7b21ce3d4996b799ce56.avif?t=1773306304\" width=616 height=123 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a small sports day of dust in a nostalgic space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge the throne by playing 3 great places, 9 exciting mini-games! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/aa323ea1af0baeaac76befd434b66f09.poster.avif?t=1773306304\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/aa323ea1af0baeaac76befd434b66f09.webm?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/aa323ea1af0baeaac76befd434b66f09.mp4?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/385ccf8d25c0cc629608efceb4151220.avif?t=1773306304\" width=616 height=107 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize dust in a variety of ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the color and material of the dust, to facial expressions, accessories, costumes, and special costumes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate it to your taste and show off your own personality! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/4a1cd31cba6333ec9c3c8a90f6cbb4ab.poster.avif?t=1773306304\" width=600 height=564 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/4a1cd31cba6333ec9c3c8a90f6cbb4ab.webm?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536600/extras/4a1cd31cba6333ec9c3c8a90f6cbb4ab.mp4?t=1773306304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
